      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "content": "### Konnect audit trail\n\nThis dashboard focuses on **control plane change events** streamed from Konnect through the audit webhook.\n\nA record appears here when Konnect logs an access event against a control plane with one of these methods:\n- `POST`\n- `PATCH`\n- `PUT`\n- `DELETE`\n\nUse the table to answer **who changed what and when**. Use the request path and target type to identify the changed Konnect resource.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "How To Read This Dashboard",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "loki",
        "uid": "loki"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "palette-classic"
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 8,
        "w": 8,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 18
      },
      "id": 3,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "orientation": "auto",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "value"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "loki",
            "uid": "loki"
          },
          "editorMode": "code",
          "expr": "sum(count_over_time({service_name=\"konnect-audit-webhook\",control_plane_change=\"true\"}[24h]))",
          "queryType": "instant",
          "refId": "A"
