      "id": 11,
      "options": {
        "content": "### Retrieve the full audit payload\n\nRun this in **Grafana Explore** against **Loki** to return the stored audit event JSON:\n\n```logql\n{service_name=\"konnect-audit-webhook\", control_plane_change=\"true\"}\n```\n\nThe stored event contains:\n- top-level fields used by the dashboard\n- `_konnect_raw` with the **entire original Konnect payload unchanged**\n- `_receiver` with local enrichment metadata\n\nTo narrow to a specific event, add one or more filters after `| json`, for example:\n\n```logql\n{service_name=\"konnect-audit-webhook\", control_plane_change=\"true\"}\n| json\n| principal_id=\"YOUR_PRINCIPAL_ID\"\n```\n\n```logql\n{service_name=\"konnect-audit-webhook\", control_plane_change=\"true\"}\n| json\n| trace_id=\"YOUR_TRACE_ID\"\n```\n\n```logql\n{service_name=\"konnect-audit-webhook\", control_plane_change=\"true\"}\n| json\n| request=~\".*core-entities/routes.*\"\n```\n\nFor full-payload inspection, expand the log line and inspect `_konnect_raw`.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Full Audit Payload Lookup",
      "type": "text"
